==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Procellarian
<hw>Pro`cel*la"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>procella</ets> a storm.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>One of a
family of oceanic birds (<fam>Procellarid⟦ae⟧</fam>) including the
petrels, fulmars, and shearwaters. They are often seen in great
abundance in stormy weather.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Procellous</ent>⟦br⟧
